productBaseInfoV1.title: White Leaf Car Freshener(75 g)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: White leaf - 0% Fragrance - Car freshnerIt is a natural Deodorizer cum air freshener made with pure form of natural raw material based activated carbon meant for specific application in car It adsorbs and eliminates odor instead of just masking itIt is free from Fragrance, Allergen and it is all natural & non -toxicIt works through the day passively and lasts for six monthsIt uses one of the most renewable natural resources in the worldIt is cent percent asthma,allergy, headache, hydrocarbon and odor free Product Description: Whiteleaf is powered by nature an science. It is filled with natural grade carbon, which is activated and carbonized at very high temperature. Most common car air fresheners either dull your senses to give illusion on freshness or try to cover up existing smell with a sickening and over powering scent.Why Whiteleaf?Just imagine the sense of Artificial lavender scent + dog musk + takeout+ cigarette smoke+,.. It is unimaginable conditions, which you were tolerating and to extent got seasoned to it. And, If you are travelling distance, your conditions will be horrible. And imagine the freshness and zeal you enjoy, when you pull over the car and get outside on seeing the lush green. You will be thinking of the change like this inside your car. Change is here, feel the nature. Having whiteleaf inside your car will remove above odors and always keeps your car free odor of pets, fuel vapour, cigarette and moisture. Whiteleaf adsorbs and eliminates the odor, rather than masking it.The Micropore activated carbon used in Whiteleaf has suitable pores, a best fit to adsorb all odor molecules. As air passes through the pores, odor particles are trapped on the surfaces inside, which purifies the air in your car. The pores and cavities work together to act like a big sponge.Have peace of mind knowing your family’s health is protected.Have peace of mind knowing you won’t ever offend your passengers with overpowering scents or fresheners that trigger their asthma or allergies.Whiteleaf is all-natural and non-toxic. It’s fragrance- and allergen- free. It’s also 100% asthma and allergy friendly.You never have to worry about the kids or the pets getting too close to Whiteleaf, because activated carbon is safe even if ingested. Still, people in many countries take activated carbon tablets as a natural alternative to break poison on intake.Whiteleaf helps to get rid of air contaminants (These contaminants causes immuno toxicity, neurotoxicity, cancer, developmental/ reproductive toxicity, and allergies) created by your fragrance air fresheners. White leaf is a cost effectiveMost common car air fresheners, in addition to being ineffective, don’t last more than 45 days. It’s a costly affair to constantly purchase refills.It works 24/7 passively, and lasts more than 180 days. It’s one of the world’s longest lasting car air freshener.Whiteleaf is 100 % Natural, Eco-Friendly and RenewableCreating a sustainable and responsible product was something that we wanted to do from the beginning.Coconut shell is one of the most renewable natural resources in the world, as it can be collected as much as possible with lowest carbon foot print of 6 months, lowest cycle than any of the natural resources.Compressed wooden board used to make the outer layer of Whiteleaf, has a much lower environmental impact, as it i s completely produced from renewable resources such as saw dust and wooden particles.After six months of usage you can cut open the Whiteleaf box and dump the activate carbon into your yard or plant pot. It will serve as a rich and natural fertilizer and insecticide for your lawn, garden or plant

It will serve as a rich and natural fertilizer and insecticide for your lawn, garden or plant
